name: Central Bank News
overview:
Central Bank News provides timely and comprehensive updates on central banking news and monetary policy developments around the globe.

Central Bank News also provides key monetary policy resources such as a table of all of the interest rates of the central banks around the world, and another table with their inflation targets.

Central Bank News started as a twitter account with one-line updates on monetary policy announcements, which has grown into a fully fledged news and intelligence website on global central banking.
